metadata.name: SuPeanz 1
metadata.description:
Introducing SuPeanz!

SuPeanz is a companion collection to Supepes and our first Free Fun Pass mint. Just like Supepes, these 4,200 SuPeanz feature every single OG SupDucks trait. However, these tadpoles are wild! It’s always the younger generation shaking things up and SuPeanz are no different. These sassy tadpoles are poppin’ out with King Frog skins, backgrounds, and their favorite toys. Come take a swim in the pond and say sup!

Follow Supepes at https://twitter.com/supepesofficial

SuPeanz was created by flatearthco.eth
Follow him on Twitter at https://twitter.com/flatearthco_eth

Learn more about SupDucks at https://supducks.com

Mad Respect goes out to https://twitter.com/twelvepepes for their dedication to sarcasm and humor in this wonderful space. Thank you.
